rolls to the section smoothly\n### Field mappings\n- Cover: `cover-photo` \u2192 `cover-images`, `appraiser1-signature` \u2192 `cover-images`\n- Photos: Group headers mapped to their respective subsections\n- Site: `site-plan-image` \u2192 `maps`\n- Zone: `zoning-map` \u2192 `maps`\n- Cert: `cert-signature` \u2192 `cover-images`\n- Sales Comps: `comp1-5-map` \u2192 `comp-maps`, `comp1-5-photo` \u2192 `comp-photos`\n- Rent Analysis: `rental-comparables-map` \u2192 `rental-comp-photos`\nAll 21 fields now display as reference links instead of upload boxes, with thumbnails when populated and navigation to the correct S3 management subsection.",
